{"tid":2024362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又老作]曼德拉基金會：搜尋逾 1500 場演說　未能證實林鄭引述名言出自曼德拉","createTime":"2020-05-19T14:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T14:31:25.000Z","uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"79664ef65d8aefd4dd214352d91b9613141893ea","tid":2024362,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/曼德拉基金會-搜尋逾-1500-場演說-未能證實林鄭引述名言出自曼德拉/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9B%BC%E5%BE%B7%E6%8B%89%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%9C%83-%E6%90%9C%E5%B0%8B%E9%80%BE-1500-%E5%A0%B4%E6%BC%94%E8%AA%AA-%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E5%90%8D%E8%A8%80%E5%87%BA%E8%87%AA%E6%9B%BC%E5%BE%B7%E6%8B%89%2F&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7vrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=b84700d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9B%BC%E5%BE%B7%E6%8B%89%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E6%9C%83-%E6%90%9C%E5%B0%8B%E9%80%BE-1500-%E5%A0%B4%E6%BC%94%E8%AA%AA-%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E5%BC%95%E8%BF%B0%E5%90%8D%E8%A8%80%E5%87%BA%E8%87%AA%E6%9B%BC%E5%BE%B7%E6%8B%89%2F&h=3d6fe000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/曼德拉基金會-搜尋逾-1500-場演說-未能證實林鄭引述名言出自曼德拉/</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥早上見記者時，引述南非已故前總統曼德拉一句「教育的崩潰足以摧毀一個國家」的名言，但隨即被質疑曼德拉根本無這說法。曼德拉基金會回應傳媒查詢時，稱搜尋過曼德拉逾 1,500 場演說及其書籍文章等，都未能找到相關言論，故不能證實此為曼德拉名言。<br />\n<br />\n法新社記者蘇昕琪在 Twitter 上貼出曼德拉基金會的回應，基金會稱搜尋過曼德拉的演說、其名言書籍，以及他撰寫過的文章，都找不到相關言論。基金會亦無法證實，名句是否如網上流傳所指曾展示於某大學入口處。<br />\n<br />\n基金會指多年以來，都遇到一些未能證實的「曼德拉名言」，而今次的「教育的崩潰足以摧毀一個國家」亦屬其中之一。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》亦正向曼德拉基金會查詢。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官辦公室傍晚指，留意到從網上搜尋，「該引述是有不同版本和出處」，樂意接受指正，若引起誤會表示歉意。特首辦又指，曼德拉有教無類的教育理念舉世公認，而教育對任何國家及地方的重要性都毋庸置疑，「特區政府同樣十分重視教育」，教育當局將繼續肩負確保教育質素的責任。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/XinqiSu/status/1262729508131495940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FXinqiSu%2Fstatus%2F1262729508131495940&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7vrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=fa916df1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FXinqiSu%2Fstatus%2F1262729508131495940&h=8048cce5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/XinqiSu/status/1262729508131495940</a>"},{"pid":"b438c1e3c970f8b4e534f52f2db2d682e418c60e","tid":2024362,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"問心 大家想唔想香港獨立建國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024303</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa1c1c680120dddefac4d0686d8145a5a22336a6","tid":2024362,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:31:25.000Z","msg":"香港新真相你識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}